snippet.title: Prisms and Pyramids [ACT 3]: How Many Triangular Pyramids Does It Take To Fill a Triangular Prism
snippet.description:
http://tapintoteenminds.com/3act-math/prisms-and-pyramids/ 
Learn about the relationship between triangular based pyramids and triangular based prisms.  How many of the pyramids will it take to fill up the prism?  This video will answer that question for you.

This is the third act of a 3 act math task called "Prisms and Pyramids"
